replies.msg:
Emery on Torreira &quot;Last season his best position was playing as a deep midfield 2. This year we're playing sometimes with just one &amp; he can achieve with his quality to get to the box &amp; get closer to score. He's very intelligent about getting space around the box &amp; taking chances&quot;<br />
<br />
Emery on Torreira: &quot;Then also, when we prepare the team to do high pressing, for us he's very important because he is very intelligent tactically, but he can play in the 2 positions. [Either as] one of the 2 midfielders [or] he can play higher for the pressing &amp; get into the box&quot;

